    Title: Lankavatara Sutra
    Locus: VII
Tags:
  - 987
---
O Mahâmati. I say unto you： During the time that elapsed between the night
of the Tathâgata's Enlightenment and the night of his entrance into Nirvâna,
not one word, not one statement was given out by him.
